<p style="text-align: center;">最近，厦门的斑马线又升级了！</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">不仅增设了 <strong><span>“人车分离”</span></strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
